    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>警告：游戏中出现的所有角色/道具均为虚构，仅作为本点击游戏的内容，请勿过度解读！</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >心爱的哥哥去踩缝纫机了，让我们通过各种方式来让他踩得更快吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富道具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过各类道具来让哥哥踩得更快！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103820/extras/dc8ba8489f885b79be3da91025b527df.poster.avif?t=1730118332\" width=452 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103820/extras/dc8ba8489f885b79be3da91025b527df.webm?t=1730118332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103820/extras/dc8ba8489f885b79be3da91025b527df.mp4?t=1730118332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得哥哥不够帅气？还有许多形象可以进行游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103820/extras/3b4c8b12a762005c7b281ca9c6f0f348.poster.avif?t=1730118332\" width=300 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103820/extras/3b4c8b12a762005c7b281ca9c6f0f348.webm?t=1730118332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103820/extras/3b4c8b12a762005c7b281ca9c6f0f348.mp4?t=1730118332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >桌宠模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让你可以一边做其他事情，一边看哥哥踩缝纫机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103820/extras/c113acfb4c3e53fa